oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Henry W. Wright, Jr. with 6 lb. 9 oz. prize bass at Fishing Rodeo in Reelfoot Lake, Tenn.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of Henry W. Wright, Jr. with a 6 lb. 9 oz. prize bass at the Fishing Rodeo, Reelfoot Lake. Wright is wearing a white hat, suspenders, button down shirt and pants with a watch on his left wrist. In the background is the lake shore and a fishing boat.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: RG 82: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
